author: @thelastmoonchild.
text:
As someone who pays attention to choreography, it really bothers me that wonyoung doesn't bend down @1:14 when the other supporting members do. And it's not just here, it's the same in every performance.  It's just like... why? It's so noticeable. I've noticed she cuts a lot of corners when it comes to choreography. She always does the bare minimum and dances at maybe, 20%. It's just a bummer because I feel like she could do SO much better if she actually put more effort in. She could be a great dancer if she wanted to be. 
And they also aren't synchronized there, as they should all be bending at the same angles. Synchronization is definitely Ive's weakness. To me, they always seem like 6 individuals dancing instead of a team. If they strengthened their synchronization with each other and moved as a unit, it would seriously benefit them during their performances. I would love to see more growth in this aspect. â¤
